        </div>

        <div class="space-y-4 text-gray-300">
          <p>
            <strong class="text-white">We are an independent comparison service.</strong> We are not a gambling operator, nor do we own any of the casinos listed on this site.
          </p>

          <p>
            This website contains affiliate links. When you click a "Play Now" button or casino link and register at that casino, we may receive a commission from the operator. This comes at no extra cost to you.
          </p>

          <div class="bg-blue-900/20 border border-blue-500/30 rounded-lg p-4 my-6">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-blue-400 mb-2 flex items-center">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
