                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="text-green-400 mr-2">‚úì</span>
                  <span>Clear disclosure of affiliate relationships</span>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="space-y-3">
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-white text-lg">How We Make Money:</h3>
              <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="text-blue-400 mr-2">‚Ä¢</span>
                  <span>Commissions when users sign up at casinos via our links</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="text-blue-400 mr-2">‚Ä¢</span>
                  <span>Revenue share based on player activity (not losses)</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="text-blue-400 mr-2">‚Ä¢</span>
                  <span>Fixed fees for featured placements (clearly marked)</span>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="border-t border-gray-700 pt-6 mt-6">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-white mb-3">Important Legal Information:</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-yellow-400 mr-2">‚ö†Ô∏è</span>
